        <mxCell id="83lpiCU1i9VFnbfGrdZY-54" value="The deamon could handle updates from the config and&lt;div&gt;then send those to the different components via dbus.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Then none of the components would have to handle&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;any of the updateing themselves and would just need to&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;have a dbus-connection to the deamon for all of their&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;IPC needs. This would also allow for easy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;inter-Component comunication.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The common lib would just hold common types and not&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;have to worry about any updating or loading of configs,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;which would all be handled by the deamon.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;It would be good to have a way for the deamon to handle&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&quot;registering&quot; different components dynamically, so that&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;the CLI could gather information about them.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="842" y="520" width="330" height="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="iHxTy6IVr4JcWS8I_kcv-1" value="Systemd:&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The individual Compoents are all to be systemd services,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;which could be either just bound to an exsisting target&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(e.g: when Hyprland starts) or we could create a custom&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;target, which might provide some more posibilities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;We also need to handle cases where the deamon crashes /&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;isn&#39;t currently running, as to not have all other widgets&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;completely fail.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="842" y="800" width="340" height="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="9mI5q9PQoPeVo3vNYNOv-7" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;endArrow=classic;endFill=1;flowAnimation=0;startArrow=classic;startFill=1;fontFamily=Garamond;" parent="1" source="9mI5q9PQoPeVo3vNYNOv-2" edge="1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="1480" y="1330" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
