        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="9mI5q9PQoPeVo3vNYNOv-28" value="&quot;SystemStateUpdater&quot; would hold what is now in &quot;SystemState&quot;&lt;div&gt;(sysinfo::System etc.) and would then be called in an interval&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;say 100ms with a refrence to SystemStateData gotten from&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;object_server.interface() (and then derefing etc.) and updated&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;the values in SystemStateData.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Possible problems:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. StateUpdater needs a lock on SystemStateData for the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;entire duration&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;of the updating. If updating hangs so does&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;everything else including other components.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;We might be&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;able to fix this by passing an InterfaceReference&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;to SystemStateUpdater and only&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;derefing etc. when we have&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;the values computed and then setting them. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;(low priority)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;2. The link between the &quot;updater&quot; and &quot;data&quot; is very loose.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font&gt;This is error-prone and might make&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;future expansion more&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;dificult, since the process might need to be repeated for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;each and every&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&quot;State-grouping&quot; we want to add.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 153, 51);&quot;&gt;(medium priority)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="842" y="1810" width="420" height="270" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
